<p style="Normal" xid="875"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="876" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“No, it's a game on the Nintendo.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="877"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="878" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“What's a Nintendo?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="879"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="880" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“The Wii?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="881"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="882" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“We, what?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="883"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="884" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Forget about Zelda, she can be a real bitch anyway. What kind of </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="885" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">spirit shards are you talking about?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="886"><c></c></p>
