<p style="Normal" xid="896"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="897" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“You don't think so?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="898"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="899" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“I don't. I haven't done it before.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="900"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="901" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">I should have known I'd hear that phrase at some point in the </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="902" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">discussion.</p>
