<p style="Normal" xid="906"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="907" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Have you talked with lots of dead people?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="908"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="909" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Not really, no. Just John back there.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="910"><c></c></p>
