<p style="Normal" xid="930" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">need to act quickly. And you need to get us some transportation. </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="931" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Hitchhiking a ride might do the trick.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="932"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="933" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Why me?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="934"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="935" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“You're the white, respectable-looking guy.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="936"><c></c></p>
