<p style="Normal" xid="2301" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">and wrecked, as if he had been carrying it in his pocket this </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2302" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">whole time.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2303"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2304" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">He looked at Adele's body with a degree of disdain that could </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2305" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">only be comparable to that shown towards a pile of dog poo, and </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2306" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">said with a gloating roar:</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2307"><c></c></p>
