<p style="Normal" xid="2309"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2310" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">I felt the enormous sorrow in Eileen's spirit when she said </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2311" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">inside my head:</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2312"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2313" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Now I remember everything.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2314"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2315" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Speaking for myself I said:</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2316"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2317" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“What do you mean everything?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2318"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2319" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“She means everything, man. Every single thing,” replied Steve </p>
