<p style="Normal" xid="2362"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2363" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Eileen had gone silent inside me, but I could tell she was </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2364" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">listening.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2365"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2366" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Some of the things, you might not like. Some of it, I'm pretty </p>
