<p style="Normal" xid="2381" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">that's been bothering me for a while.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2382"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2383" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Yeah, well?” I said, and though I had some suspicions, I </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2384" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">couldn't believe it even when I heard it from his own mouth:</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2385"><c></c></p>
