<p style="Normal" xid="2387" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">choked on a chicken bone and almost died, for the fourth time </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2388" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">that day.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2389"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2390"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2391"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2392" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">I was sipping at some sludge that Steve had made insisting it was </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2393" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">coffee, and though a large array of scientific tests could </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2394" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">factually prove he might have been telling the truth, I could not </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2395" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">think of it as anything other than a cup of swamp water with some </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2396" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">mud thrown in for flavor. He made lousy coffee, but perfect </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2397" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Heimlich maneuvers.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2398"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2399" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">We had been talking for the better part of an hour, old Mama </p>
