<p style="Normal" xid="2480" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">adventurous; I had just done this job at a small but profitable </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2481" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">motel. I had gate crashed this wild party where anything seemed </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2482" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">normal enough, and while I was drunk off my mind, mostly on the </p>
