<p style="Normal" xid="2976"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2977" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Was it? Tasted like rat's piss, I think,” said Steve with as </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2978" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">much naivety as his face could express wearing a piece of </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2979" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">underwear around his head with a dick-shaped carrot tied to it.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2980"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2981" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“So you're wasted?”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2982"><c></c></p>
