<p style="Normal" xid="2988" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">because even though she wasn't herself, she wasn't mad anymore </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2989" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">either.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2990"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2991" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Yeah, and then we fought these ninjas, man. And I killed one, </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2992" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">look. Got blood on my skunk.”</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2993"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2994" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“No, don't do that, not here. Not now, please,” I said and I </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2995" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">sighed.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2996"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2997" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Steve looked at me as if gazing through thick fog, not being able </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2998" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">to see a god-damn thing. He then pointed the skunk towards me and </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="2999" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">said, apparently confused, wide-eyed and drunk like a wine taster </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3000" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">at a marathon event without a spitoon:</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3001"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3002" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">“Elvis! Man, I love you. Y'know? Not in that way, no. Never. Big </p>
