<p style="Normal" xid="3016" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">as rain before you know it,” I said trying to sound convincing. </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3017" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">Hearing the words coming out of my mouth, they sounded just like </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3018" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">what an estate property agent would have said to a couple of </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3019" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">newlyweds: that the old, haunted house that caught fire back in </p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3020" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">'89 and is now used as a meth lab by a gang of homicidal junkies </p>
