<p style="Normal" xid="3077" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">her. And hope.</p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3078"><c></c></p>
<p style="Normal" xid="3079" props="text-align:left; dom-dir:ltr">One could have said that things were ticking along with military </p>
